0.75.name: wordpress/tweet-manager
0.75.description:
Create Your Own Custom Twitter Application and Publish to Your Twitter account 'Via Your Custom Twitter Application'. Plugin creates a Custom Post Type called 'tweets' where you can save commonly used messages with links and videos to save time. Plugin can read rss feeds, and allow you to post them to your Twitter account.

Developers Website: http://MyWebsiteAdvisor.com Developers Plugin Page: http://MyWebsiteAdvisor.com/tools/wordpress-plugins/tweet-manager/

Check out the Tweet Manager WordPress Plugin Setup Tutorial Video:

Requirements:

  1. Twitter Account
